    <note>Zhou(1) Shunyuan [17448] See documentation for father-in-law, Wang(2) Boxiang [17444]. In 1166, he was prefect of Shaozhou (Guangdong) and erected a shrine to Zhou(1) Dunyi [504] and used the two Cheng(2) brothers [3102] [3105] as his equal. He was probably a member of Zhou(1) Dunyi's lineage. CBD, 2, 1491.</note>
